premise_source_doc_sentence: According to Nielsen Media Research , `` Sexual Healing '' was seen by 3.7 million households , making it the most watched South Park premiere since `` Rainforest Shmainforest '' in 1999 , and helping make March 17 the most-watched night of the year for Comedy Central to that point .

`` Sexual Healing '' parodies several elements of the Woods scandal , including alleged fights with his wife Elin Nordegren , which are portrayed as part of a new Tiger Woods PGA Tour video game played by Cartman , Stan , and Kenny .
